title: Fix: no notification for user when plan illegal
message:
Fix: no notification for user when plan illegal

Can happen e.g. when website is not displaying the actual plan, but something like "Leider ist unser Server ausgefallen"
Now: When the plan cannot be found, the text for the information-textView and the widgets are updated and after opening the app, WebActivity is started and a toast is shown
